<h2>Client Wellbeing Status Update</h2>

<p>Dear {{counselorName}},</p>

<p>A wellbeing status change has been detected for your client <strong>{{clientName}}</strong>.</p>

<div style="background: {{statusColor}}; border-left: 4px solid {{statusBorderColor}}; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0;">
  <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Status Change:</h3>
  <p><strong>Previous Status:</strong> {{oldStatus}}</p>
  <p><strong>Current Status:</strong> {{newStatus}}</p>
  <p><strong>Detected:</strong> {{timestamp}}</p>
</div>

{{#if isCritical}}
<div style="background: #fee; border: 2px solid #f00; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0;">
  <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #c00;">⚠️ Immediate Attention May Be Required</h3>
  <p>This status indicates your client may be experiencing significant distress.</p>
</div>
{{/if}}

<p>Please review the client's recent counseling sessions to assess their current situation and determine if additional support is needed.</p>

<p style="margin-top: 30px;">
  <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}/counselor/clients/{{memberId}}"
     style="background: #0891b2; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block;">
    View Client Dashboard
  </a>
</p>

<p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
  <strong>In Crisis?</strong> Remind clients to call <strong>988</strong> (Suicide & Crisis Lifeline) or <strong>911</strong> for immediate help.
</p>
